stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_deprecated: current_epoch >= FULU_FORK_EPOCH + MIN_EPOCHS_FOR_BLOB_SIDECARS_REQUESTS
    q_check_deprecated --> q_fully_deprecated: fully deprecated
    q_check_deprecated --> q_compute_range: in transition period
    q_fully_deprecated --> [*]: respond empty or reject
    q_compute_range --> q_range: serve_range = [min(current_epoch - MIN_EPOCHS, FULU_FORK_EPOCH), FULU_FORK_EPOCH)
    q_range --> q_check_request_range: requested range intersects serve_range
    q_check_request_range --> q_respond_empty: range entirely at or after FULU_FORK_EPOCH
    q_check_request_range --> q_serve_sidecars: range includes pre-Fulu epochs
    q_respond_empty --> [*]: respond with empty list
    q_serve_sidecars --> [*]: respond with blob sidecars from serve_range
